"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-arts-entertainment-tv-news-olympics-adam-peaty-bbc-b2587571.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  British swimmer won silver in the men's breastroke final  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 355, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9998271130991996, \"rank\": 0.00015623304887681916, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Olympicsviewers have called out theBBC's decision to endlessly show emotional montages of British swimmerAdam Peatyin its coverage.\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 470, \"end\": 477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9998271130991996, \"rank\": 0.00015623304887681916, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"BBC One repeatedly aired clips of the athlete in the build-up toPeaty competing in the men's breastroke finalon Sunday (28 July).\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 642, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 513, \"end\": 520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.311943365963104e-17, \"text\": \"BBC One\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The racesaw the 29-year-old narrowly miss a third successive Olympic gold- he ended up winning silver in the race, trailing Italy's\\u00a0Nicol\\u00f2 Martinenghi by just 0.02 of a second.\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 767, \"end\": 772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6241903249072375, \"rank\": 0.6020385302367274, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 775, \"end\": 793, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicol\\u00f2_Martinenghi\", \"score\": 0.9999999647136526, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nicol\\u00f2 Martinenghi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicol\\u00f2_Martinenghi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicol\\u00f2_Martinenghi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One moving montage shown in the lead-up had seen Peaty's family's sharing their support for the swimmer, who's had a tough few years with periods of depression and problems with alcohol.\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 1007, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He has described himself as having a \\\"self-destructive spiral\\\", partly brought on by the breakdown of his relationship with the mother of his young son.\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1160, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While many said they found the insight into Peaty's life poignant and beautiful, lots of viewers thought the coverage was overkill.\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1293, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"No offence, but I have seen this Adam Peaty montage about three times today,\\\" one person shared on X.\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1397, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1329, \"end\": 1339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Yes, he's great and his story inspiring, but come on!\\\"\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1453, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A second person added: \\\"It's like a drinking game without the booze: every time the BBC shows an Adam Peaty clip, turn over to Eurosport.\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1592, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1539, \"end\": 1542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.6208448961181965, \"rank\": 0.5924671677220952, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 1552, \"end\": 1562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course he is a fantastic champion and I hope he wins, but too much!\\\"\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1664, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The BBC are obsessed with Adam Peaty,\\\" wrote a third.\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1720, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1671, \"end\": 1674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.6208448961181965, \"rank\": 0.5924671677220952, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 1693, \"end\": 1703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"